main_body:
Commission Regulation (EC) No 858/2003 is amended as follows:
1. in the title, the words "flying a flag of a Member State with the exception of Denmark and the United Kingdom" are replaced by "flying the flag of certain Member States";
2. in the first and second subparagraphs of Article 1, the words "with the exception of Denmark and the United Kingdom" are replaced by "with the exception of Denmark, Germany, the Netherlands and the United Kingdom".
